    "name": "Mystery Box: Hidden Secrets",
    "steam_appid": 1735790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/eb198f765681d4943712817449a43951.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/eb198f765681d4943712817449a43951.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To unlock the boxes of this escape room game, you have to interact with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. You can find puzzle pieces on the side of the boxes as well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/32ad8ac79e6beb8730d62278493aee2e.poster.avif?t=1770031498\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/32ad8ac79e6beb8730d62278493aee2e.webm?t=1770031498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/32ad8ac79e6beb8730d62278493aee2e.mp4?t=1770031498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/b1c83b977c0078d366b0fddc5a5256c1.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/b1c83b977c0078d366b0fddc5a5256c1.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span>The illusion of holding a real object in total darkness is compelling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/b3e20d8cb6336c52a5c4b3c03fefdb09.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/b3e20d8cb6336c52a5c4b3c03fefdb09.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span>Once you open all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and find a brief history of the discovered invention. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/5afffdd2cca186eebc25886f6ee61dc4.poster.avif?t=1770031498\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/5afffdd2cca186eebc25886f6ee61dc4.webm?t=1770031498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/5afffdd2cca186eebc25886f6ee61dc4.mp4?t=1770031498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think outside of the box to solve all enigmas, it's not always an easy job to escape the rooms! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/a8a7f442f9ea68a066c9bbb42799c200.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/a8a7f442f9ea68a066c9bbb42799c200.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/dd38af61a8155cd0922ec098244e6c92.poster.avif?t=1770031498\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/dd38af61a8155cd0922ec098244e6c92.webm?t=1770031498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/dd38af61a8155cd0922ec098244e6c92.mp4?t=1770031498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/0f7fdbf2ea49b96d78ff169f9494b094.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/0f7fdbf2ea49b96d78ff169f9494b094.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game with your headphones on to get immersed in this amazing adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/d1bf53d3c3a4ef283ff9a44653870575.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/d1bf53d3c3a4ef283ff9a44653870575.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span>Got stuck on some riddle? Tap the bulb button to get a helpful hint! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/da31888562d4b38cb6876cb1b6355d01.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/da31888562d4b38cb6876cb1b6355d01.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span>Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1770031498\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1770031498 width=800 height=212 /></span>Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong> here. I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing everything myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p>",
